Split a column composed of nested lists into multiple columns.

Source: R/extract_from_hmmer.R
extract_from_hmmer.Rd

Split a column composed of nested lists into multiple columns.

extract_from_hmmer(data, column = "hits.domains")

Arguments

data

Dataframe whose column is going to be splitted.

column

Column to split.

Value

A DataFrame with columns column splitted into several columns.

Examples

data(phmmer_2abl)
extract_from_hmmer(
    data = phmmer_2abl,
    column = "hits.domains"
)
